  "3294690": {
    "name": "缘结甜祇 ~My Sweet Goddess~",
    "steam_appid": 3294690,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由日本美少女游戏知名厂商ALcot开发，JAST负责发行的轻松甜蜜日常向视觉小说《缘结甜祇~My Sweet Goddess~》正式登录STEAM！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一个关于魔神转世体与女神们的日常纯爱故事！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/9badad05e2f94b88a457e03a6c079805.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/9badad05e2f94b88a457e03a6c079805.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=132 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发：ALcot</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发行：JAST</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原画：しらいちご ／ すいみゃ ／ ひさまくまこ ／ みけおう ／ あおなまさお（ＳＤ）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景：空下 元 ／ モーリー</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG：春ノ瀬 史</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐：AngelNote</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/3325f54a80bdba36146b1052202ce12f.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/3325f54a80bdba36146b1052202ce12f.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=132 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人界今天也很和平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类不知道奇迹的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更不知道神界发生的众神之战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间来到西历20××年，秋天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经在神界大闹的魔神的转世体，鸣川隼斗，来到马萨德新城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隼斗的母亲、再生女神的爱丽丝，告诉儿子：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“在人界积累善行，偿还前世的罪过。那样的话就能回到神界了。”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隼斗遵循母亲的教诲，成长为品行端正、认真严肃的青年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是，魔神的诅咒给隼斗带来苦难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就在他打算在新的城镇开始平静生活的时候，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阴差阳错地，亲上了黑帮千金无花果美命的嘴唇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这样下去会被误解，积累的善行将功亏一篑！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为一个吻而开始转动的命运齿轮，与前世羁绊让隼斗烦恼不已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女神系妈妈、恋爱脑的黑道千金、笨手笨脚的班长、单纯的狗耳少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甜蜜而奇妙的缘分让魔神转世体与这些女孩子结识，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日常喧闹又略带忧伤的<strong>“恋爱神话”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就这样拉开了帷幕——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/ffb3c6ca0e60f8c8af785d413138ab6a.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/ffb3c6ca0e60f8c8af785d413138ab6a.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=132 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/ece323cd5aff3d58193fc9b86b6c8fc5.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/ece323cd5aff3d58193fc9b86b6c8fc5.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/3d5187122cf6379b3b89b9970fcda3aa.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/3d5187122cf6379b3b89b9970fcda3aa.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/8ecf188dc4b0c735dac2d1db90a8ed03.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/8ecf188dc4b0c735dac2d1db90a8ed03.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/fcbea175d347df48c0e59f996b516e88.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/fcbea175d347df48c0e59f996b516e88.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/6c10a16c956940e13ffc02b83ddb6d7d.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/6c10a16c956940e13ffc02b83ddb6d7d.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/08636221653d16adbb18faab642bd322.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/08636221653d16adbb18faab642bd322.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras/c55e54ef0c509e67cbbcc4a1d3d227ff.avif?t=1760098063\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294690/extras_big/c55e54ef0c509e67cbbcc4a1d3d227ff.avif?t=1760098063 width=800 height=132 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作除男主人公外均有配音，4位女主角可单独调整音量大小</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持按键设置，可按照个人习惯调整快捷操作设定</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作共有四个结局，根据你不同的选择，后续剧情可能会走向不同的结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻略完毕的角色在游戏开始页面可直接进入路线选择</p></li></ul>",
